snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Oracle of Secrets
snippet.description:
---Read first: This is simply a tech demo. It was never intended to be a full game. Also, the z3.zfgc.com link is down, but you can check it out here: http://www.nintendocfc.com/NCFC10/index.php?act=viewb&id=18
My main channel is: https://www.youtube.com/user/SuperRobotGames 
and my LP/Whatever channel is: https://www.youtube.com/user/TTDPLetsPlay
----

Bending dimensions and mastering forbidden secrets, Link must embark on his most perilous journey yet.

View the booth at z3.zfgc.com

EDIT:
Oh hey, 1000 views :3 Nice.
8000 views, holy hell.
